# Groups [/groups]

Groups enable collaborative recommendations.

## List My Groups [GET /groups/me]

Returns groups where the authenticated user is a member.

+ Request
    + Headers
            Authorization: Bearer <token>

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (array[Group])

## Create Group [POST /groups]

Creates a group. The authenticated user becomes a member (and typically host).

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
            Authorization: Bearer <token>
    + Attributes (GroupCreate)

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Group)

## Get Group [GET /groups/{groupId}]

+ Parameters
    + groupId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)

+ Request
    + Headers
            Authorization: Bearer <token>

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Group)

## Update Group [PATCH /groups/{groupId}]

Updates group name and/or status.

+ Parameters
    + groupId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
            Authorization: Bearer <token>
    + Attributes (GroupUpdate)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Group)

## Delete Group [DELETE /groups/{groupId}]

+ Parameters
    + groupId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)

+ Request
    + Headers
            Authorization: Bearer <token>

+ Response 204

## Join Group With Code [POST /groups/join]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
            Authorization: Bearer <token>
