# Group Sessions [/groups/{groupId}/sessions]

A group session represents a "movie night" workflow.
Sessions can have:
- `context` (mood, maxDuration, preferred/excluded genres)
- soft-start timeouts
- started status
Recommendations can be gated by questionnaire readiness.

## List Group Sessions [GET /groups/{groupId}/sessions]

+ Parameters
    + groupId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)

+ Request
    + Headers
            Authorization: Bearer <token>

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (array[GroupSession])

## Create Group Session [POST /groups/{groupId}/sessions]

+ Parameters
    + groupId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
            Authorization: Bearer <token>
    + Attributes (GroupSessionCreate)

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Attributes (GroupSession)

## Get Group Session [GET /groups/{groupId}/sessions/{sessionId}]

+ Parameters
    + groupId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)
    + sessionId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)

+ Request
    + Headers
            Authorization: Bearer <token>

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (GroupSession)

## Update Group Session [PATCH /groups/{groupId}/sessions/{sessionId}]

+ Parameters
    + groupId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)
    + sessionId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
            Authorization: Bearer <token>
    + Attributes (GroupSessionUpdate)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (GroupSession)

## Start Group Session [POST /groups/{groupId}/sessions/{sessionId}/start]

Marks the session as started.

+ Parameters
    + groupId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)
    + sessionId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)

+ Request
    + Headers
            Authorization: Bearer <token>

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (GroupSession)

## Get Group Soft-Start Status [GET /groups/{groupId}/softstart-status]

Returns current soft-start status for a group (used by UI to show countdown/readiness).

+ Parameters
    + groupId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)

+ Request
    + Headers
            Authorization: Bearer <token>

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (GroupSoftStartStatus)

