# PCS Recommendations [/pcs]

Process Centric Services (PCS) orchestrate multiple internal/external services
to generate a final recommendation result.

## Recommend For User [POST /pcs/recommend/user]

Returns a personalized recommendation for the authenticated user.
Uses preferences, watch history signals, and TMDB candidate pools.

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
            Authorization: Bearer <token>
    + Attributes (PCSUserRecommendRequest)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (UserRecommendationResult)

## Recommend For Group [POST /pcs/recommend/group]

Returns group recommendations. The requester must be a group member.
If `sessionId` is provided, the engine checks readiness gates.

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
            Authorization: Bearer <token>
    + Attributes (PCSGroupRecommendRequest)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (GroupRecommendationResult)

---

# Movies [/movies]

Movie endpoints are backed by a TMDB adapter. Responses are normalized for the UI.

## Search Movies [GET /movies/search?query={query}&page={page}]

+ Parameters
    + query: `interstellar` (string)
    + page: 1 (number, optional)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (TMDBMovieListResponse)

## Get Trending Movies [GET /movies/trending?page={page}]

+ Parameters
    + page: 1 (number, optional)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (TMDBMovieListResponse)

## Get Popular Movies [GET /movies/popular?page={page}]

+ Parameters
    + page: 1 (number, optional)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (TMDBMovieListResponse)

## Get Now Playing Movies [GET /movies/now-playing?page={page}]

+ Parameters
    + page: 1 (number, optional)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (TMDBMovieListResponse)

## Get Top Rated Movies [GET /movies/top-rated?page={page}]

+ Parameters
    + page: 1 (number, optional)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (TMDBMovieListResponse)

## Get Movie Details [GET /movies/{id}]

+ Parameters
    + id: 550 (number) - TMDB movie id

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (TMDBMovieDetails)

## Get Similar Movies [GET /movies/{id}/similar?page={page}]

+ Parameters
    + id: 550 (number)
    + page: 1 (number, optional)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (TMDBMovieListResponse)

## Get Recommended Movies [GET /movies/{id}/recommended?page={page}]

+ Parameters
    + id: 550 (number)
    + page: 1 (number, optional)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (TMDBMovieListResponse)

## Get Movie Watch Providers [GET /movies/{id}/providers]

Returns availability/providers info (streaming/rent/buy) by region.

+ Parameters
    + id: 550 (number)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (TMDBWatchProvidersResponse)

## List Genres [GET /movies/genres]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (TMDBGenreListResponse)

