# Data Structures

## HealthStatus (object)
+ status: `ok` (string)
+ service: `watchwise-backend` (string)

## User (object)
+ id: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)
+ email: `john@example.com` (string)
+ username: `johnny` (string)
+ avatar: `avatar_01` (string)
+ authProvider: `google` (string) - `google` | `github`
+ createdAt: `2024-01-01T12:00:00Z` (string)
+ updatedAt: `2024-01-01T12:00:00Z` (string)

## UserUpdate (object)
+ username: `johnny` (string, optional)
+ avatar: `avatar_01` (string, optional)

## PreferenceEvent (object)
+ id: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)
+ userId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)
+ type: `genre` (string) - `genre` | `actor` | `director` | `mood` | `energy` | `company` | `duration` | `novelty`
+ value: `Action` (string) - Value label (e.g., "Action", "Christopher Nolan")
+ weight: 0.8 (number) - Strength in [0..1] or similar scale
+ source: `explicit` (string) - `explicit` | `questionnaire`
+ createdAt: `2024-01-01T12:00:00Z` (string)

## PreferenceEventCreate (object)
+ type: `genre` (string)
+ value: `Action` (string)
+ weight: 0.8 (number, optional)
+ source: `explicit` (string, optional)

## PreferenceEventBulkCreate (object)
+ events: (array[PreferenceEventCreate])

## GroupQuestionnaireStatus (object)
+ groupId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)
+ members: (array[GroupMemberQuestionnaireStatus])

## GroupMemberQuestionnaireStatus (object)
+ userId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)
+ completed: true (boolean)
+ lastEventAt: `2024-01-01T12:00:00Z` (string, optional)

## WatchHistoryEntry (object)
+ id: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)
+ userId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)
+ movieId: `tmdb:550` (string)
+ watchedAt: `2024-01-01T12:00:00Z` (string)
+ rating: 8 (number, optional)
+ completed: true (boolean)

## WatchHistoryCreate (object)
+ movieId: `tmdb:550` (string)
+ watchedAt: `2024-01-01T12:00:00Z` (string, optional)
+ rating: 8 (number, optional)
+ completed: true (boolean, optional)

## WatchHistoryUpdate (object)
+ watchedAt: `2024-01-01T12:00:00Z` (string, optional)
+ rating: 8 (number, optional)
+ completed: true (boolean, optional)

## UserList (object)
+ id: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)
+ userId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)
+ name: `Favorites` (string)
+ slug: `favorites` (string)
+ isDefault: false (boolean)
+ items: (array[ListItem], optional)
+ createdAt: `2024-01-01T12:00:00Z` (string)
+ updatedAt: `2024-01-01T12:00:00Z` (string)

## UserListCreate (object)
+ name: `Favorites` (string)
+ slug: `favorites` (string, optional)

## UserListUpdate (object)
+ name: `Favorites` (string, optional)
+ slug: `favorites` (string, optional)

## ListItem (object)
+ movieId: `tmdb:550` (string)
+ addedAt: `2024-01-01T12:00:00Z` (string)

## ListItemCreate (object)
+ movieId: `tmdb:550` (string)

## Group (object)
+ id: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)
+ name: `Movie Night` (string)
+ members: (array[string]) - User IDs
+ hostId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string, optional)
+ joinCode: `JOIN123` (string, optional)
+ joinCodeExpiresAt: `2024-01-01T13:00:00Z` (string, optional)
+ status: `open` (string, optional)
+ createdAt: `2024-01-01T12:00:00Z` (string)
+ updatedAt: `2024-01-01T12:00:00Z` (string, optional)

## GroupCreate (object)
+ name: `Movie Night` (string)

## GroupUpdate (object)
+ name: `Movie Night` (string, optional)
+ status: `open` (string, optional) - `open` | `locked` | other states if used by the UI

## GroupJoinRequest (object)
+ code: `JOIN123` (string)

## GroupJoinCodeResponse (object)
+ joinCode: `JOIN123` (string)
+ joinCodeExpiresAt: `2024-01-01T13:00:00Z` (string)

## GroupSession (object)
+ id: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)
+ groupId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)
+ context: (RecommendationContext)
+ selectedMovieId: `tmdb:550` (string, optional)
+ softStartAt: `2024-01-01T12:30:00Z` (string, optional)
+ softStartTimeoutMinutes: 15 (number, optional)
+ startedAt: `2024-01-01T12:45:00Z` (string, optional)
+ status: `pending` (string, optional)
+ createdAt: `2024-01-01T12:00:00Z` (string)
+ updatedAt: `2024-01-01T12:10:00Z` (string, optional)

## GroupSessionCreate (object)
+ context: (RecommendationContext, optional)

## GroupSessionUpdate (object)
+ context: (RecommendationContext, optional)
+ selectedMovieId: `tmdb:550` (string, optional)
+ softStartAt: `2024-01-01T12:30:00Z` (string, optional)
+ softStartTimeoutMinutes: 15 (number, optional)
+ status: `started` (string, optional)

## GroupSoftStartStatus (object)
+ groupId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)
+ active: true (boolean)
+ softStartAt: `2024-01-01T12:30:00Z` (string, optional)
+ remainingSeconds: 420 (number, optional)

## RecommendationContext (object)
+ mood: `happy` (string, optional)
+ preferredGenres: (array[string], optional)
+ excludedGenres: (array[string], optional)
+ maxDuration: 120 (number, optional)

## PCSUserRecommendRequest (object)
+ context: (RecommendationContext, optional)
+ limit: 20 (number, optional)
+ offset: 0 (number, optional)

## PCSGroupRecommendRequest (object)
+ groupId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string)
+ sessionId: `663b2f1e9c1d2a001e8e4f1a` (string, optional)
+ context: (RecommendationContext, optional)
+ limit: 20 (number, optional)
+ offset: 0 (number, optional)

## UserRecommendationResult (object)
+ recommended: (ScoredMovie)
+ topK: (array[ScoredMovie])

## GroupRecommendationResult (object)
+ buckets: (GroupBuckets)
+ outsiders: (array[GroupScoredMovie], optional)

## GroupBuckets (object)
+ high: (array[GroupScoredMovie])
+ medium: (array[GroupScoredMovie])
+ explore: (array[GroupScoredMovie])

## ScoredMovie (object)
+ movie: (MovieCandidate)
+ score: 0.87 (number)
+ reasons: (array[string])
+ serendipity: false (boolean, optional)

## GroupScoredMovie (object)
+ movie: (MovieCandidate)
+ score: 0.87 (number)
+ reasons: (array[string])
+ compatibility: 0.73 (number)
+ outsider: false (boolean)

## MovieCandidate (object)
+ movieId: `tmdb:550` (string)
+ title: `Fight Club` (string)
+ posterPath: `/a26cQPRhJPX6GbWfQbvZdrrp9j9.jpg` (string, optional)
+ releaseDate: `1999-10-15` (string, optional)
+ popularity: 60.0 (number, optional)
+ rating: 8.4 (number, optional)

## TMDBMovie (object)
+ id: 550 (number)
+ title: `Fight Club` (string)
+ release_date: `1999-10-15` (string, optional)
+ popularity: 60.0 (number)
+ vote_average: 8.4 (number)
+ vote_count: 25000 (number)
+ poster_path: `/a26cQPRhJPX6GbWfQbvZdrrp9j9.jpg` (string, optional)

## TMDBMovieListResponse (object)
+ page: 1 (number)
+ results: (array[TMDBMovie])

## TMDBMovieDetails (object)
+ id: 550 (number)
+ title: `Fight Club` (string)
+ poster_path: `/a26cQPRhJPX6GbWfQbvZdrrp9j9.jpg` (string, optional)
+ vote_average: 8.4 (number, optional)
+ original_language: `en` (string, optional)
+ overview: `A ticking-time-bomb insomniac...` (string, optional)
+ runtime: 139 (number, optional)
+ release_date: `1999-10-15` (string, optional)

